{"tid":2283930,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"衛詩寫新詩：時間是最佳調味料","createTime":"2020-11-13T02:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T05:10:19.000Z","uid":272819,"like":15,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4afa77642894626646c38521ec46f3f540f52550","tid":2283930,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:45:17.000Z","msg":"不論醃製、煲湯、整麵包都好<br />\n時間越耐味道越突出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頓時飲一碗家人煲既老火令湯 <br />\n冬日裡你便捧著碗湯 合上雙眼 緩緩傾下冒著白煙、由時間調配的熱湯 <br />\n頓時嘴角微微上揚 發出「呀！」的一聲 原來時間真是神奇的東西！<br />\n尢其是家人煲的湯 那種溫暖和愛是其他餐館不能帶給你的<br />\n然而除了食物以外與人相處亦需要時間作調味<br />\n日子久了 情深亦濃<br />\nTime is the best seasoning for everything<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAlthough time flies, it contains the finest flavour to us<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> forever"},{"pid":"4fb28fd7ab66f5b233f14e6068a99d80840298fb","tid":2283930,"uid":93096,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:47:11.000Z","msg":"好文彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9187cc3ccdec464d21c3dc663548a39f7c74da0","tid":2283930,"uid":260581,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:47:13.000Z","msg":"好文采<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83305d2493e658987908b99865a72d1a8a75106","tid":2283930,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4fb28fd7ab66f5b233f14e6068a99d80840298fb","tid":2283930,"uid":93096,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:47:11.000Z","msg":"好文彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:47:37.000Z","msg":"謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eedaa5e878e5e4890f403f281381b678d86847d2","tid":2283930,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fb28fd7ab66f5b233f14e6068a99d80840298fb","tid":2283930,"uid":93096,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:47:11.000Z","msg":"好文彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447fd3c97e3895d18be54dfbfb7db4432126ee07","tid":2283930,"uid":272819,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a9187cc3ccdec464d21c3dc663548a39f7c74da0","tid":2283930,"uid":260581,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:47:13.000Z","msg":"好文采<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />謝城巴 煮野食是要有耐心"},{"pid":"dd0857986676acd98c6eaa1c6eacb5e7cd1bf676","tid":2283930,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"eedaa5e878e5e4890f403f281381b678d86847d2","tid":2283930,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fb28fd7ab66f5b233f14e6068a99d80840298fb","tid":2283930,"uid":93096,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:47:11.000Z","msg":"好文彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77eff3f6d0d83ed00aa207c48b3dd405ce77451a","tid":2283930,"uid":272819,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:49:04.000Z","msg":"邊條粉腸負皮ME?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca8955f1825d6791ca23e17bc52895234e9e0a7","tid":2283930,"uid":357936,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:49:24.000Z","msg":"似散文多D，不過都支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972565b45a51f8812dfb67a3789dbb8b53c6aa87","tid":2283930,"uid":33359,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:49:27.000Z","msg":"但時間在蘭姨身上落得太重手了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b184a1bb1396c1c82ba73b95a968665e946a80","tid":2283930,"uid":272819,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4ca8955f1825d6791ca23e17bc52895234e9e0a7","tid":2283930,"uid":357936,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:49:24.000Z","msg":"似散文多D，不過都支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:49:47.000Z","msg":"係 我抒情<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d6a57e9168d277bbe2062aa8af4f12517fdbb7","tid":2283930,"uid":272819,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"972565b45a51f8812dfb67a3789dbb8b53c6aa87","tid":2283930,"uid":33359,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:49:27.000Z","msg":"但時間在蘭姨身上落得太重手了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:50:15.000Z","msg":"印伯冇文采 淨係會咸濕其他清流女子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336ab6758f1ba9073f0ae968f57eea2768717704","tid":2283930,"uid":33359,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"87d6a57e9168d277bbe2062aa8af4f12517fdbb7","tid":2283930,"uid":272819,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"972565b45a51f8812dfb67a3789dbb8b53c6aa87","tid":2283930,"uid":33359,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:49:27.000Z","msg":"但時間在蘭姨身上落得太重手了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:50:15.000Z","msg":"印伯冇文采 淨係會咸濕其他清流女子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:50:47.000Z","msg":"蘭姨是青樓女子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d923980ef15625ea88aa447736b9cc2c928cc199","tid":2283930,"uid":219470,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:51:00.000Z","msg":"今天不小心把心愛的水杯打碎了<br />\n事後我用了十五分鐘去細心欣賞<br />\n發現打碎了的玻璃碎<br />\n竟然比起平日那個形態更美<br />\n然後我再用了十分鐘去打掃地方<br />\n再為其拍照<br />\n<br />\n這短短的三十分鐘<br />\n算是今天我思緒最安穩的時間<br />\n打碎了的水杯<br />\n是我今天看過最美好的東西<br />\n而那水杯著地的那一聲<br />\n是聽過最美好的聲音<br />\n<br />\n原來人生覺得最爛的事情<br />\n也未必是最糟<br />\n因為最糟的<br />\n可能一直就在眼前而未曾發現<br />\n又或者根本就是自己<br />\n我想我找到了答案"},{"pid":"c50d13b528daa73dd678c577fcaefbbb0b51d070","tid":2283930,"uid":286700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:51:19.000Z","msg":"但係時間愈耐,　人就會死<br />\n死係咪都係調味料?"},{"pid":"b6837ea8b71563f6029ccda0929f632ff74060d0","tid":2283930,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:52:23.000Z","msg":"但對一個人耐咗會淡然無味"},{"pid":"e4edea46f19d96e36b3565a2ed93e6780460a5d2","tid":2283930,"uid":272819,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"336ab6758f1ba9073f0ae968f57eea2768717704","tid":2283930,"uid":33359,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"87d6a57e9168d277bbe2062aa8af4f12517fdbb7","tid":2283930,"uid":272819,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"972565b45a51f8812dfb67a3789dbb8b53c6aa87","tid":2283930,"uid":33359,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:49:27.000Z","msg":"但時間在蘭姨身上落得太重手了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:50:15.000Z","msg":"印伯冇文采 淨係會咸濕其他清流女子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:50:47.000Z","msg":"蘭姨是青樓女子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:52:43.000Z","msg":"詩係純樸小姑娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不容你隨便咸濕"},{"pid":"96bad1dbfca966cae188f303dc4187bf561a9b5c","tid":2283930,"uid":50196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:52:58.000Z","msg":"我想識你女朋友"},{"pid":"aeb59a8487c2979f1c5a8b0d48fedbb86f75d26a","tid":2283930,"uid":272819,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c50d13b528daa73dd678c577fcaefbbb0b51d070","tid":2283930,"uid":286700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:51:19.000Z","msg":"但係時間愈耐,　人就會死<br />\n死係咪都係調味料?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:53:06.000Z","msg":"是 讓你學會珍惜味道"},{"pid":"b09280f84d9f31659f3a7c2d2b2344f312f0de8d","tid":2283930,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b6837ea8b71563f6029ccda0929f632ff74060d0","tid":2283930,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:52:23.000Z","msg":"但對一個人耐咗會淡然無味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:53:31.000Z","msg":"是 所以間唔中要換下口味"},{"pid":"ce414798380089dd1e82473c59f36a46a9f01fba","tid":2283930,"uid":272819,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"96bad1dbfca966cae188f303dc4187bf561a9b5c","tid":2283930,"uid":50196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:52:58.000Z","msg":"我想識你女朋友"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:53:47.000Z","msg":"我想how村你門口"},{"pid":"ceeeefc0c73382fa4cd738518fdd7d83dceb0411","tid":2283930,"uid":50196,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ce414798380089dd1e82473c59f36a46a9f01fba","tid":2283930,"uid":272819,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"96bad1dbfca966cae188f303dc4187bf561a9b5c","tid":2283930,"uid":50196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:52:58.000Z","msg":"我想識你女朋友"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:53:47.000Z","msg":"我想how村你門口"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:55:01.000Z","msg":"衫洗得更透"},{"pid":"5bbabc32c47f3813047c1e1a47f7aa617f6a80f0","tid":2283930,"uid":49270,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:55:32.000Z","msg":"韓寒：<br />\n<br />\n前兩天這裡在爭吵詩不詩的問題，沒看，覺得奇怪。因為我的觀點一直是現代詩歌和詩人<br />\n都沒有存在的必要的，現代詩這種體裁也是沒有意義的。這年頭紙挺貴，好好的散文，寫<br />\n在一行裡不好嗎？古詩的好在於他有格式，格式不是限制，就像車一定要開在指定路線的<br />\n賽道裡一樣，才會有觀眾看，你撒開花了到處亂開，這不就是交通現狀嗎，觀眾自己瞎開<br />\n也能開成那樣，還要特地去看你瞎開？這就是為什麼發展到現在詩歌越來越淪落。因為它<br />\n已經不是詩，但詩人還以為自己在寫詩。<br />\n<br />\n寫散文就寫散文，散文家這個名稱自然沒有詩人那麼好騙文學女青年。好好的標點符號擺<br />\n在那，你非不用，先把自己大腦搞抽筋了，然後把句子給腰斬了，再揉碎，跟彩票開獎一<br />\n樣隨機一排，還真以為自己是藝術家了。千萬別拿徐志摩的輕輕的和海子的春暖花開跟我<br />\n說事，寫了幾十年句子出幾句順口的也是應該的。但是，總體來說，我覺得現代詩的最多<br />\n價值只能作為歌詞的一個小分支存在。既然沒有格式了，那有寫歌詞的人就行了，還要詩<br />\n人做什麼。<br />\n<br />\n從上學開始我看見圖書館裡的現代詩集就是這觀點，永遠不會變了，如果數學習題冊像現<br />\n代詩集那樣排就好了，打草稿的地方全有了。在我所有的小說裡，每本都不忘要諷刺現代<br />\n詩一下，然後自己寫一首，還真有沒看明白的讀者以為我喜歡現代詩。所以今天就說的直<br />\n白一點，最後，我要賦現代詩一首<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小詩一首<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n飛機上落枕<br />\n<br />\n小<br />\n<br />\n或者詩<br />\n<br />\n一首還是兩首<br />\n<br />\n今天晚上的脖子<br />\n<br />\n特<br />\n<br />\n別疼<br />\n<br />\n是<br />\n<br />\n飛機上睡落枕了<br />\n<br />\n還是<br />\n<br />\n飛機被我睡落枕了<br />\n<br />\n他說<br />\n<br />\n以後寫<br />\n<br />\n散文<br />\n<br />\n再散<br />\n<br />\n再散<br />\n<br />\n也別忘記了<br />\n<br />\n要用標點符<br />\n<br />\n號<br />\n<br />\n唷"},{"pid":"6541fc5ded9b0cc05b6975ccaabb79fe48fd6267","tid":2283930,"uid":272819,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ceeeefc0c73382fa4cd738518fdd7d83dceb0411","tid":2283930,"uid":50196,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ce414798380089dd1e82473c59f36a46a9f01fba","tid":2283930,"uid":272819,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"96bad1dbfca966cae188f303dc4187bf561a9b5c","tid":2283930,"uid":50196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:52:58.000Z","msg":"我想識你女朋友"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:53:47.000Z","msg":"我想how村你門口"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:55:01.000Z","msg":"衫洗得更透"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:56:22.000Z","msg":"鹽過雙河否野你奈久<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b03156e48e5df2a8c88ec1ae198088ed15bfd3","tid":2283930,"uid":51346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:56:41.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"eeaa2549a8b7926d601c9c87dfa4b3d19381ce00","tid":2283930,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bbabc32c47f3813047c1e1a47f7aa617f6a80f0","tid":2283930,"uid":49270,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:55:32.000Z","msg":"韓寒：<br />\n<br />\n前兩天這裡在爭吵詩不詩的問題，沒看，覺得奇怪。因為我的觀點一直是現代詩歌和詩人<br />\n都沒有存在的必要的，現代詩這種體裁也是沒有意義的。這年頭紙挺貴，好好的散文，寫<br />\n在一行裡不好嗎？古詩的好在於他有格式，格式不是限制，就像車一定要開在指定路線的<br />\n賽道裡一樣，才會有觀眾看，你撒開花了到處亂開，這不就是交通現狀嗎，觀眾自己瞎開<br />\n也能開成那樣，還要特地去看你瞎開？這就是為什麼發展到現在詩歌越來越淪落。因為它<br />\n已經不是詩，但詩人還以為自己在寫詩。<br />\n<br />\n寫散文就寫散文，散文家這個名稱自然沒有詩人那麼好騙文學女青年。好好的標點符號擺<br />\n在那，你非不用，先把自己大腦搞抽筋了，然後把句子給腰斬了，再揉碎，跟彩票開獎一<br />\n樣隨機一排，還真以為自己是藝術家了。千萬別拿徐志摩的輕輕的和海子的春暖花開跟我<br />\n說事，寫了幾十年句子出幾句順口的也是應該的。但是，總體來說，我覺得現代詩的最多<br />\n價值只能作為歌詞的一個小分支存在。既然沒有格式了，那有寫歌詞的人就行了，還要詩<br />\n人做什麼。<br />\n<br />\n從上學開始我看見圖書館裡的現代詩集就是這觀點，永遠不會變了，如果數學習題冊像現<br />\n代詩集那樣排就好了，打草稿的地方全有了。在我所有的小說裡，每本都不忘要諷刺現代<br />\n詩一下，然後自己寫一首，還真有沒看明白的讀者以為我喜歡現代詩。所以今天就說的直<br />\n白一點，最後，我要賦現代詩一首<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小詩一首<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n飛機上落枕<br />\n<br />\n小<br />\n<br />\n或者詩<br />\n<br />\n一首還是兩首<br />\n<br />\n今天晚上的脖子<br />\n<br />\n特<br />\n<br />\n別疼<